high_descs: Walk half way to the wall in front of you then turn right and walk to the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock closest to you.
Adjust your position all the way to the right of where you're standing now so you are looking at the desk by the wall with a clear bowl in front of you.
Put the alarm clock below the remote in front of you.
Walk back to where you got the first alarm clock.
Pick up the other alarm clock on the desk.
Walk back over to where you put the first alarm clock.
Put the alarm clock in your hands on the desk to the right of the first alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Put two alarm clocks on the desk.

high_descs: Move towards the mirror on the wall then turn to the right and move to the desk to the right of the green recycling bin.
Pick up the brown alarm clock to the right of the pencil and nearest to the front edge of the table.
Turn right and move towards the map of Europe on the wall then turn left and move to the desk with the laptop computer on it.
Place the alarm clock to the right of the laptop and in front of the remote control on the desk.
Turn to the right and move toward the window and then turn right when between the two wooden chairs and move toward the space between the table and the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock in front of the lamp on the table.
Turn to the right and move toward the map on the wall and then turn left and face the desk with the laptop computer.
Place the alarm clock in front of the glass bowl and also to the right of the alarm clock already on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place two alarm clocks on the desk.

high_descs: Move to the smaller desk to the left of the bigger desk
Pick up the closest clock off of the smaller desk
Move to the right side of the larger desk
Place the clock to the right of the laptop on the desk
Move to the smaller desk to the left again
Pick up the second clock from off the smaller desk
Move to the right side of the bigger desk.
Place the second clock next to the first.
anns.task_desc: Move the two clocks from the smaller desk to the full size desk.
